H0.text: If you were given a facsimile of the Venus Rosewater Dish, what would you have won. Australian Open Women's Championship

H1.text: If you were given a facsimile of the Venus Rosewater Dish, what would you have won. French Open Women's Singles Title

H2.text: If you were given a facsimile of the Venus Rosewater Dish, what would you have won. US Open Women's Singles Championship

H3.text: If you were given a facsimile of the Venus Rosewater Dish, what would you have won. Wimbledon Ladies' Singles Title

A4.text: The Venus Rosewater Dish is the Ladies' Singles Trophy awarded at The Championships, Wimbledon, and was first presented in 1886.

A5.text: The names of the winners from 1884 to 1957 are inscribed on the inside of the dish, and the names of 1958 to present on the outside.
